70
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,359
Run slowly.

71
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,079
Get down.

72
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,359
Alright.

73
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:26,640
