201
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,640
OK. Please wait a minute.

202
00:14:07,479 --> 00:14:10,159
The total cost of your flowers, package,

203
00:14:10,239 --> 00:14:11,159
drinks and room

204
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,320
